name: we can talk about the future
description: After a few days of living together, a new color, a new sound began to flow in my heart, I thought it was better to open up and say everything I feel, unfortunately this triggered a lot of sadness in our situation, it's complicated to feel something so strong for her, I just wanted to bring you peace and love, shattered now i keep looking for the pieces on the floor, i really wanted a hug from alice now. i know love is a good thing
